obson">{{Cite news |url= |title=UFOs, ghosts, crop circles: sceptics fight back; Fifty years ago, an American pilot spotted flying saucers. Now gullibility seems to have taken over. Roger Dobson talks to some doubters |author=Roger Dobson |work=[[The Independent]] |date=22 June 1997 }}</ref> || English || 1997 || [[Association for Skeptical Enquiry]] || Michael Heap |- | ''[[Skeptical Inquirer]]''<ref name="AFU"/> || English || 1976 || [[Committee for Skeptical Inquiry]] (formerly CSICOP) || [[Kendrick Frazier]] |- | ''[[Skeptic (U.S. magazine)|Skeptic]]'' (''Skeptic Magazine'')<ref name="AFU"/> || English || 1992 || [[The Skeptics Society]] || [[Michael Shermer]] |- | ''[[Gesellschaft zur wissenschaftlichen Untersuchung von Parawissenschaften#Publications, blogs and social media|Skeptiker]]''<ref name="AFU"/> || German || 1987 || [[Gesellschaft zur wissenschaftlichen Untersuchung von Parawissenschaften]] || Inge Hüsgen |- | ''Skeptikernytt''<ref name="AFU"/> || Norwegian || 1992<ref name="AFUmags"/> || Skepsis Norge || Terje Emberland<ref name="AFUmags"/> |- | ''Skeptikko''<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.skepsis.fi/Yhdistys/MikaSkepsisOn/SkepsisinEnglish.aspx |title=Skepsis in English |work=Skepsis ry website |publisher=[[Skepsis (organization)|Skepsis ry]] |accessdate=6 December 2014}}</ref> || Finnish || 1988 || [[Skepsis ry]] || Risto K. Järvinen |- | ''The Arizona Skeptic''<ref name="AFU"/> || English || 1987<ref name="AFUmags"/> || Phoenix Skeptics || |- | ''The Beacon''<ref name="AFUmags"/> || English || 1988 || East Bay Skeptics Society || |- | ''The Gateway Skeptic''<ref name="AFUmags"/> || English || 1990 || || |- | ''The New England Journal of Skepticism''<ref name="AFUmags"/> || English || 1998 || [[New England Skeptical Society]] || [[Steven Novella]] |- | ''The New York Skeptic''<ref name="AFUmags"/> || English || 1988 || New York Area Skeptics || |- | ''[[The Skeptic (Australian magazine)|The Skeptic]]''<ref name="AFU"/> || English || 1981 || [[Austra